data.chText: 薄纱，纱罗（通常由棉或丝织成）
data.enText: a type of light transparent cloth, usually made of cotton or silk
a type of thin cotton cloth used for covering and protecting wounds
material made of a network of wire; a piece of this

means: 薄纱，纱罗(通常由棉或丝织成)

tr: a net of transparent fabric with a loose open weave
(medicine) bleached cotton cloth of plain weave used for bandages and dressings

value.def: Gauze is a type of light, soft cloth with tiny holes in it.

example.ex: Strain the juice through a piece of gauze or a sieve.
example.tran: 用一块纱布或过滤网将果汁过滤一下。
